---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import LegacyHeader from '../components/LegacyHeader.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import ContactSection from '../components/ContactSection.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Answer Engine Optimisation Services | Bright Forge SEO" description="Search is changing fast. Our AEO services help Philippine brands appear in AI answers, voice queries, and zero-click results where users now look.">
  <LegacyHeader slot="header" />
  
  <!-- Enhanced Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero-aeo-services">
    <!-- Animated Background Elements -->
    <div class="hero-bg-elements">
      <div class="floating-circle circle-1"></div>
      <div class="floating-circle circle-2"></div>
      <div class="floating-circle circle-3"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Enhanced Breadcrumbs -->
      <nav class="hero-breadcrumbs">
        <a href="/" class="breadcrumb-link">Home</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-separator">›</span>
        <span class="breadcrumb-current">Answer Engine Optimization Services Philippines</span>
      </nav>
      
      <div class="hero-container">
        <!-- Hero Content -->
        <div class="hero-content">
          <!-- Hero Badge -->
          <div class="hero-badge">
            <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
            <span>AEO Specialists</span>
          </div>
          
          <h1>Answer Engine Optimization <span>(AEO) Services</span></h1>
          
          <p>The Future of Search is Answers. Are You Providing Them?</p>
          
          <p>Traditional SEO is no longer enough. To win in today's search landscape, you need to be the definitive answer. Bright Forge SEO's Answer Engine Optimization (AEO) services position your brand as the go-to authority in the Philippines and beyond.</p>
          
          <p>In a world of voice assistants, AI-powered summaries, and instant-answer boxes, your customers are no longer just searching—they're asking questions. AEO is the science and art of ensuring your business is the one that provides the answer, directly and authoritatively.</p>
          
          <p>Our <strong>Answer Engine Optimization Philippines</strong> services help businesses dominate featured snippets and voice search results with <strong>professional AEO strategies</strong>. From voice search optimization to AI-powered content, we position your brand as the definitive answer source as your trusted <strong>AEO partner</strong>, so you can capture more visibility and traffic.</p>
          
          <!-- Hero Actions -->
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/contact" class="cta-button primary">
              <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
              <span>Get Your Free AEO Analysis</span>
            </a>
            <a href="#why-aeo" class="cta-button secondary">
              <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
              <span>Learn About AEO</span>
            </a>
          </div>
          

        </div>
        
        <!-- Hero Visual -->
        <div class="hero-visual">
          <div class="hero-image-container">
            <div class="aeo-icon-grid">
              <div class="aeo-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-microphone"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="aeo-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="aeo-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-comments"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="aeo-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-magic"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="aeo-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="aeo-icon">
                <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Old SEO Strategy is Falling Behind Section -->
  <section class="challenges-section" id="why-aeo">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Your Old SEO <span>Strategy is Falling Behind</span></h2>
        <p>The way we search has fundamentally changed. Users expect immediate, concise answers, and search engines have evolved to deliver them.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="challenges-content">
        <div class="challenge-text">
          <p>This has led to a rise in "zero-click searches," where the user's query is answered directly on the search results page, eliminating the need to click on a website.</p>
          <p>If your digital strategy isn't optimized for this new reality, you're becoming invisible. Are you experiencing any of these challenges?</p>
          
          <ul class="challenges-list">
            <li>Your competitors consistently appear in featured snippets and "People Also Ask" boxes.</li>
            <li>Your website traffic has plateaued or is in decline, despite your ranking efforts.</li>
            <li>Your brand is non-existent on voice search platforms like Google Assistant, Siri, and Alexa.</li>
            <li>You feel unprepared for the impact of AI Overviews and other AI-driven search technologies.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p>If you nodded along to any of these points, you're not alone. Many businesses are struggling to adapt. The good news is, there's a clear path forward.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="challenge-image">
          <img src="/images/old-seo-vs-aeo.svg" alt="Traditional SEO vs Answer Engine Optimization" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Competitive Edge Section -->
  <section class="edge-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Gain a Competitive Edge with <span>Answer Engine Optimization (AEO)</span></h2>
        <p>Answer Engine Optimization is the next evolution of SEO. It's a holistic strategy designed to make your content the most direct, relevant, and authoritative answer to your audience's questions.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="edge-content">
        <p>While traditional SEO focuses on ranking your website, AEO focuses on making your content the featured result.</p>
        <p>Our AEO services target the most valuable real estate in modern search:</p>
        
        <div class="services-grid">
          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Featured Snippets & "People Also Ask"</h3>
            <p>The coveted "Position Zero" at the very top of search results.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-microphone"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Voice Search Results</h3>
            <p>Becoming the audible answer on smart speakers and mobile assistants.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-project-diagram"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>Google's Knowledge Graph</h3>
            <p>Appearing in the authoritative information panels for key industry topics.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-icon">
              <i class="fas fa-robot"></i>
            </div>
            <h3>AI Overviews</h3>
            <p>Being a primary source for the AI-generated summaries that are transforming search.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="edge-conclusion">By optimizing for answers, we don't just aim for a link — we aim for direct visibility and brand recognition.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Complete AEO Solution Section -->
  <section class="solution-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Your Complete <span>AEO Solution</span></h2>
        <p>At Bright Forge SEO, we've developed a comprehensive AEO methodology to position our clients as industry leaders. Our process is transparent, data-driven, and tailored to the unique needs of the Philippine market.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="solution-content">
        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>AEO Strategy & Discovery</h3>
              <p>We begin with a deep dive into your business, your target audience, and their most pressing questions. We conduct a thorough analysis to identify your "answer gaps" and uncover the most significant opportunities for AEO success.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Conversational Keyword & Question Research</h3>
              <p>We move beyond basic keywords to uncover the specific questions, phrases, and natural language queries your customers are using in voice and text search. This allows us to create content that directly matches user intent.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3><a href="/content-seo-services-philippines">Content Optimization for Answers</a></h3>
              <p>We re-engineer your existing content and create new, targeted pieces designed to be easily digestible by both users and answer engines. This includes creating robust FAQ sections, utilizing a clear question-and-answer format, and adopting a concise, conversational tone.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3><a href="/technical-seo-services-philippines">Technical SEO & Schema Markup</a></h3>
              <p>This is the technical backbone of AEO. We implement advanced structured data (Schema.org markup), including FAQPage, HowTo, and Speakable schema. This code translates your content into a language that search engines can easily understand and feature.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">5</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Google Business Profile Optimization</h3>
              <p>For businesses in the Philippines, local visibility is paramount. We optimize your Google Business Profile to dominate local search queries, ensuring you're the answer for customers in your area.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">6</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Performance Monitoring & Reporting</h3>
              <p>AEO is not a "set it and forget it" service. We continuously track your performance in featured snippets, voice search rankings, and other AEO placements. You'll receive clear, actionable reports that demonstrate the tangible impact of our work.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Benefits Section -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Tangible Benefits of <span>Becoming the Answer</span></h2>
        <p>Investing in AEO delivers a powerful return on investment by fundamentally enhancing your digital presence.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-trophy"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Dominate "Position Zero"</h3>
          <p>Leapfrog your competition by securing the most prominent position on the search results page.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Increase Brand Authority & Trust</h3>
          <p>Being the source of the definitive answer establishes your brand as a credible and trustworthy expert.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Drive Highly Qualified Traffic</h3>
          <p>Attract users who are actively seeking the solutions, products, or services you provide.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Future-Proof Your Digital Strategy</h3>
          <p>Stay ahead of the curve as search continues its evolution towards AI and natural language processing.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Capture Voice Search Traffic</h3>
          <p>Be the answer on the growing number of smart speakers and mobile voice assistants used by Filipinos every day.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-card">
          <div class="benefit-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Enhance Local Visibility</h3>
          <p>Become the go-to choice for customers in your geographic area, from Manila to Mindanao.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us Section -->
  <section class="choose-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Choose <span>Bright Forge SEO?</span></h2>
        <h3 class="subtitle">Your AEO Experts in the Philippines</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="choose-grid">
        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-map-marked-alt"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Local Market Expertise</h3>
          <p>We have an in-depth understanding of the nuances of the Filipino market and the search behavior of your local customers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Data-Driven Approach</h3>
          <p>Our strategies are built on a foundation of meticulous research, competitor analysis, and performance data, not guesswork.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Transparent Partnership</h3>
          <p>We believe in complete transparency. You'll always know what we're doing, why we're doing it, and the results we're achieving.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="choose-card">
          <div class="choose-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
          </div>
          <h3>Proven Results</h3>
          <p>We are committed to delivering measurable improvements that impact your bottom line.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Frequently Asked <span>Questions about AEO</span></h2>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What is the difference between AEO and traditional SEO?</h3>
          <p>Think of AEO as a specialized, more advanced form of SEO. While traditional SEO focuses on improving your website's overall ranking in a list of results, AEO focuses on getting your content featured as the direct answer to a user's query. They work best together.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How long does it take to see results from AEO?</h3>
          <p>The timeline for seeing results can vary depending on your industry's competitiveness and the current state of your website. However, some gains, like securing featured snippets for long-tail questions, can be achieved within a few months.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Is AEO relevant for my industry?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely. If your customers ask questions online, AEO is relevant for you. Whether you're in e-commerce, B2B services, healthcare, or hospitality, positioning yourself as the answer provides a significant competitive advantage.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Will AEO replace traditional SEO?</h3>
          <p>No, AEO will not replace traditional SEO. A strong technical foundation, quality backlinks, and a good user experience are still crucial. AEO is an essential layer on top of a solid SEO strategy that prepares you for the future of search.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="cta-container">
        <h2>Ready to Become the Go-To Answer in Your Industry?</h2>
        <p>Stop chasing rankings and start owning the conversation. Let's talk about how our Answer Engine Optimization services can transform your online visibility and drive sustainable growth for your business.</p>
        <a href="/contact/" class="cta-button">Get Your Free AEO Analysis</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <ContactSection />

  <Footer slot="footer" />
</MainLayout>

<style>
/* Enhanced Hero Section - AEO Services */
.hero-aeo-services {
  position: relative;
  padding: 120px 0 100px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #FF6B35 30%, #FF6B35 70%, #4285F4 100%);
  background-size: 400% 400%;
  animation: gradientShift 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  overflow: hidden;
}

@keyframes gradientShift {
  0%, 100% {
    background-position: 0% 50%;
  }
  50% {
    background-position: 100% 50%;
  }
}

/* Floating Background Elements */
.hero-bg-elements {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  pointer-events: none;
  z-index: 1;
}

.floating-circle {
  position: absolute;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.circle-1 {
  width: 120px;
  height: 120px;
  top: 20%;
  right: 15%;
  animation-delay: 0s;
}

.circle-2 {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  top: 60%;
  right: 25%;
  animation-delay: 2s;
}

.circle-3 {
  width: 60px;
  height: 60px;
  top: 40%;
  right: 8%;
  animation-delay: 4s;
}

@keyframes float {
  0%, 100% {
    transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg);
  }
  33% {
    transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(120deg);
  }
  66% {
    transform: translateY(10px) rotate(240deg);
  }
}

/* Hero Container */
.hero-container {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: center;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}

/* Breadcrumbs */
.hero-breadcrumbs {
  display: inline-block !important;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  line-height: 1;
  position: relative;
  z-index: 10;
}

.hero-breadcrumbs * {
  display: inline !important;
  vertical-align: baseline !important;
}

.breadcrumb-link {
  color: white !important;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  opacity: 0.9;
}

.breadcrumb-link:hover {
  opacity: 1;
  text-decoration: underline;
}

.breadcrumb-separator {
  color: white !important;
  margin: 0 8px;
  opacity: 0.7;
}

.breadcrumb-current {
  color: white !important;
  font-weight: 600;
}

/* Hero Content */
.hero-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}

/* Hero Badge */
.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  padding: 8px 16px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: white;
  font-weight: 500;
}

.hero-badge i {
  font-size: 14px;
}

/* Hero Title */
.hero-content h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: white;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.hero-content h1 span {
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
}

/* Hero Text */
.hero-content p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.hero-content p:first-of-type {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

/* Hero Actions */
.hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1rem;
  margin: 2rem 0;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.cta-button {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border-radius: 50px;
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 1rem;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.cta-button.primary {
  background: white;
  color: #f97316;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.cta-button.primary:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

.cta-button.secondary {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  color: white;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
}

.cta-button.secondary:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* FontAwesome Icon Fixes */
.aeo-icon i {
  font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free" !important;
  font-weight: 900 !important;
  font-style: normal !important;
  font-variant: normal !important;
  text-rendering: auto !important;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale !important;
  display: inline-block !important;
  color: white !important;
  font-size: 1.5rem !important;
}

.hero-badge i {
  font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free" !important;
  font-weight: 900 !important;
  font-style: normal !important;
  font-variant: normal !important;
  text-rendering: auto !important;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale !important;
  display: inline-block !important;
  color: white !important;
}

.cta-button i {
  font-family: "Font Awesome 5 Free" !important;
  font-weight: 900 !important;
  font-style: normal !important;
  font-variant: normal !important;
  text-rendering: auto !important;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale !important;
  display: inline-block !important;
}

/* Hero Stats */
.hero-stats {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2rem;
  margin-top: 3rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.stat {
  text-align: center;
}

.stat-number {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: white;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
  font-weight: 500;
}

/* Hero Visual */
.hero-visual {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
}

.hero-image-container {
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

/* AEO Icon Grid */
.aeo-icon-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 1.5rem;
  max-width: 300px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.aeo-icon {
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 20px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.aeo-icon:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .hero-container {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .hero-visual {
    order: -1;
  }
  
  .hero-stats {
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .aeo-icon-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .aeo-icon {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
  }
  
  .floating-circle {
    display: none;
  }
  
  .hero-actions {
    justify-content: center;
  }
}

/* Challenges Section Styles */
.challenges-section {
  padding: 80px 0;
  background: white;
}

.section-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.section-header h2 {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #1a1a1a;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  line-height: 1.2;
}

.section-header h2 span {
  color: #f97316;
}

.section-header p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  color: #666;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.challenges-content {
